{
  "stem": "19807.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, a few hours later, the-- the head of the police, the chief of police came over.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were assembled.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He went on the steps of the-- of the school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's where we were assembled.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he said, Jews, go home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Your lives have been spared.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[CRYING]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What happened was in-- in Bulgaria during the war, through an edict of the king, they conscripted all male Jews from age of 19 or 20 to age of 55 or 50, I don't remember exactly, they're conscripted into the [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it was under paramilitary organization, where they would go-- they were wearing uniforms, really.",
      "word_count": 58
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were called [NON-ENGLISH], [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they would go and build roads and build bridges.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And under that-- under that pretext, the king was able, whenever the Jews were asked to be sent to the camps, when the Germans would insist on asking to be sent to the camps-- now, this is told to me by my mother and this is told to me by my father.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I have no firsthand knowledge, only-- that's the only knowledge I have, and-- which I verified everything after that with-- with the clergy on my trip recently.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But what they did is they-- they-- they dispersed the Jews from Sofia, which were 25,000, all over to the smaller cities.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there, they conscripted the males so they can build bridges and they can build roads.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So the excuse of the king was always, well, I need the Jews to build roads.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And those roads are being built for you, for the Nazis, so they can go through Bulgaria quicker.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
